{"word":"στεναχίζω","slug":"στεναχίζω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>στεναχίζω</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>epic <a href='S:lengthened'>lengthd.</a> form of <a href='S:στενάχω'><el>στενάχω</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b>only in <a href='S:present tense'>pres.</a> and <a href='S:imperfect tense'>imperf.</a> <i>to sigh, groan, wail</i>, <b><a href='S:Homer'>Hom.</a></b>:—so in <a href='S:Medium, Middle'>Mid.</a>, <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><a href='S:transitive'>trans.</a> <i>to bewail, lament</i>, <b><a href='S:Odyssey'>Od.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}